Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.03,0:17:06.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这儿会永远一团乱下去了\N{\fs38}the whole place was gonna be messed up for good,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.68,0:17:07.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但你做到了\N{\fs38}but here you did it
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.96,0:17:11.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你一如既往地想出了个疯办法\N{\fs38}you figured out that crazy solution, like you always do.
