Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.84,0:17:21.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,能把螺丝刀递给我\N{\fs38}Will you hand me a screwdriver
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.88,0:17:24.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,让我完成我的离子除颤器吗\N{\fs38}so I can finish my ionic de-defibulizer?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.43,0:17:25.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,当然 Rick\N{\fs38}Sure thing, Rick.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.49,0:17:26.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,给你\N{\fs38}Here's a screwdriver.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.97,0:17:27.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好了 Morty\N{\fs38}All right, Morty.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.60,0:17:29.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢你\N{\fs38}Thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.13,0:17:30.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拧一下\N{\fs38}We got one screw turn...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.54,0:17:33.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拧两下\N{\fs38}and two screw turns... and...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.84,0:17:40.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好了 Morty 我们到了\N{\fs38}All right, Morty, here we are.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.15,0:17:42.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,天啊 Rick 那是我们吗\N{\fs38}Oh, my god, Rick! Is that us?!
