Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.08,0:17:50.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,- 不行 我接受不了  - 冷静下来 Morty\N{\fs38}- No, I can't deal with this! - Calm yourself, Morty.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.70,0:17:52.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,- 这种事我受不了 Rick  - 冷静 Morty\N{\fs38}- I can't deal with this, Rick! - Calm down, Morty.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.25,0:17:54.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,- 骗人的吧  - 冷静下来 Morty\N{\fs38}- This can't be real!  - You got to calm down, Morty.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.24,0:17:55.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我我我我们被炸碎了\N{\fs38}W-w-w-w-we're ripped apart!
