Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.75,0:17:59.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没事的 \N{\fs38}It's fine. Everything is fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.68,0:18:02.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有无数个平行的现实 Morty\N{\fs38}There's an infinite number of realities, Morty
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.04,0:18:03.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在一小部分平行世界里 我运气好\N{\fs38}and in a few dozen of those, I got lucky
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.84,0:18:05.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,让一切恢复了原状\N{\fs38}and turned everything back to normal.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.14,0:18:06.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我只需要找到其中某一个世界\N{\fs38}I just had to find one of those realities
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.78,0:18:09.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们俩刚好在这段时间里死了\N{\fs38}in which we also happen to both die around this time.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.23,0:18:10.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在我们只需要悄悄取代\N{\fs38}Now we can just slip into the place of
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.87,0:18:13.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个世界里死掉的自己 就没问题了\N{\fs38}our dead selves in this reality and everything will be fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.91,0:18:15.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就和什么都没发生过一样 Morty\N{\fs38}We're not skipping a beat, Morty.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.61,0:18:16.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,来帮我搬下尸体\N{\fs38}Now, help me with these bodies.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.77,0:18:17.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这太疯狂了\N{\fs38}This is insane.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.54,0:18:18.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Morty 我搬我自己\N{\fs38}Look, Morty, I'll grab myself,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.86,0:18:19.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你搬你自己 行吗\N{\fs38}you grab yourself, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.93,0:18:21.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我觉得这样挺公平的\N{\fs38}I mean, t-t-t-that seems fair to me, I mean,
