Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.13,0:18:25.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那我们以前的世界呢\N{\fs38}Rick, what about the reality we left behind?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.63,0:18:28.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那Hilter找了治愈癌症方法的世界呢 Morty\N{\fs38}What about the reality where Hitler cured cancer, Morty?
