Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.69,0:18:31.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,反正这种办法也不是每周都能用\N{\fs38}It's not like we can do this every week, anyways.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.62,0:18:33.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,最多就用个三四次\N{\fs38}We get three or four more of these, tops.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.38,0:18:35.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把你自己的尸体搬起来 \N{\fs38}Now, pick up your dead self and come on.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.38,0:18:36.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,欲速则不达\N{\fs38}Haste makes waste.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.76,0:18:38.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然我觉得你没注意到这个细节\N{\fs38}I-I-I don't suppose you've considered this detail,
